{"tid":2273030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警卧底破黑幫和勝和拉153人，曾涉元朗7.21恐襲「姑爺偉」再被捕","createTime":"2020-11-05T12:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T15:33:57.000Z","uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4fca6c9fb2f3beefb5749e62d6931892b52c5082","tid":2273030,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"鑑於黑幫和勝和在上水及元朗積極擴張其勢力，警方新界北總區刑事部去年6月至今於區內進行代號「截擊」的反三合會行動，派出卧底滲入黑幫搜集證據，經一年半時間見時機成熟，上月中開始採取行動，在多個處所拘捕153人，包括102男51女。警方指被捕黑幫涉及年息達1,140厘的高利貸活動、刑毀、刑恐、經營非法賭博場所等罪行，被捕者最細為年僅15歲學生(涉傷人案)。消息稱，警方今次行動中拘捕了和勝和黑幫上水白頭福及元朗姑爺偉等骨幹成員，其中在南邊圍一帶活躍的「姑爺偉（張Ｘ偉）」，去年10月已曾因為涉及「元朗7.21」事件而曾被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201105/FKQTSNDNIJAZZIBZKGJADIV3B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201105%2FFKQTSNDNIJAZZIBZKGJADIV3B4%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8t5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=90c81e40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201105%2FFKQTSNDNIJAZZIBZKGJADIV3B4%2F&h=7f18642c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201105/FKQTSNDNIJAZZIBZKGJADIV3B4/</a>"},{"pid":"13c4071b444635686f3aba8a688530b7bd3334f7","tid":2273030,"uid":238370,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c95817e5355b21c48bdd7e14fb6930fb62212d","tid":2273030,"uid":30791,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"一丘之貉"},{"pid":"10284c949356e35afbe47ea4be928d30692d8ef6","tid":2273030,"uid":284432,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9972a32ab02c16b5cd6e267878a6e6abc70fd2b","tid":2273030,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"香港都割韮菜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p